{"tid":2060653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[612 一週年] 一百年前嘅韓國烈士有啲嘢同大家講","createTime":"2020-06-11T22:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T11:34:38.000Z","uid":144676,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44517d7c9968ec93b63ba7b5136df417813d9fa2","tid":2060653,"uid":144676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T22:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbVwSij.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbVwSij.gif&h=8bf31058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1920年韓國<strong>三一運動</strong>一週年，喺監獄入面嘅<strong>柳寬順</strong>帶領人民抗議及記念死難者。同年9月，只有17歲嘅柳寬順被嚴刑拷打致死，多年後被追封為獨立烈士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wYXFRS8dlzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwYXFRS8dlzk&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0phbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1a6fdae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wYXFRS8dlzk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt10276054/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt10276054%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0phbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1b8611a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imdb.com/title/tt10276054/</a>"},{"pid":"2f6eac5f4587adc4cc5b8354f7dd0ad7ca9922fc","tid":2060653,"uid":144676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T22:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2eb507e0df8a5afc81253738ec752b6cc5bde1","tid":2060653,"uid":144676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T22:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3ddd2a48f8e46c0d35426ece9c05da8d72d253","tid":20606